/blockquote><br />\n食邊隻? 嚴重個時食治敏速"},{"pid":"f8f0e179378bc54d2e6e2495627b238398d7957b","tid":222973,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年365日隨時黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出入冷氣地方都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要靠食藥先控制到 不過一食藥就超攰超眼訓</blockquote><br />\n抗敏感藥好多時都會眼訓<br />\n所以我都唔敢成日食<br />\n由其返工果陣"},{"pid":"3d2d30bb3f99704c694dded310d52270d1c50c1b","tid":222973,"uid":27694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"兩年前 兩邊鼻輪住塞<br />\n兩前年冬天轉季開始 每分每秒都塞住 無論任何地方 係兩邊一齊塞<br />\n不過就少鼻水 但有鼻水果日會全日流唔停"},{"pid":"5bc6f56fac2cc9fc832225a591d69ae8d2474bf4","tid":222973,"uid":12433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得係香港空氣有問題<br />\n我去咗外國讀書未試過<br />\n一返香港就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  夏天返黎出機場嗰下我覺得自己抖唔到氣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3966af31161f8000965c633cebe673e2f338cd4c","tid":222973,"uid":11991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"轉天氣特別嚴重 夜晚個鼻一定會塞到醒<br />\n然後鼻敏感搞到眼又痕埋一份<br />\n勁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"624384fb7d945b151369f656cb8595c9b28f09fe","tid":222973,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci